title: Should the MutantsDAO enable the possibility to display purchased NFTs into metaverse galleries?
body: OnCyber is offering a service recently introduced, adding the possibility for DAO owners to create a fractionalized ERC1155 version out of vaulted ERC721 NFTs. This allows holders of fractionalized NFTs to see and use the original NFTs inside metaverse galleries (or other integrated services). We could be the first DAO showing their vault in a metaverse gallery!
author: 0xa11435b21e0Eff08A6c2c5b8316ACC94054e8bAB
